  "keyFeatures": [
    "Parse and read Source 2 compiled resource files (models, textures, materials, maps, sounds, particles, etc.)",
    "Export textures to PNG/TGA/DDS formats with channel manipulation and cubemap support",
    "Export models and maps to glTF 2.0 format with animations, materials, and physics",
    "Decompile materials, maps, and other resources to human-readable formats",
    "Read and extract files from VPK archives using ValvePak library",
    "Parse binary KeyValues (KV1, KV3) formats",
    "Decode compiled shaders and convert SPIRV bytecode",
    "Handle texture compression formats (BC1-BC7, ETC2, ASTC)",
    "Support for 80+ Source 2 resource types",
    "Cross-platform .NET library with CLI tool"
  ],
